reviewText: The item was defective.  But, the seller refunded the credit back into my account.

I love the Weakest Link and Anne Robinson, and this is a fun game to play. Sure, it's not as exciting as the real deal, but it's fun to pretend that you're getting humorously put down by the Queen of Mean. Now, if only I could find a group of eight other people, it'd be a party...
This is my favorite game show ever, so I was miffed when it wouldn't work. It does not even begin playing at all. Horrible. Just... horrible! You ARE The Weakest DVD! Goodbye!
My son asked for it. he likes it, played with it for about two weeks. I guess it's worth the money.
